{"__ud_title":"NorthCombat 模组开发","__ud_tags":[],"__ud_update_time":1782225614908,"__ud_create_time":1782225613416,"__ud_draft":false,"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":1,"id":"NorthCombat-模组开发"},"content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"NorthCombat 模组开发"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在 Minecraft 里复刻出接近现代战术射击体验的模组——"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"NorthCombat"},{"type":"text","text":"，这个想法诞生已经有一段时间了。我目前把整个模组的交互、功能模块、网络协议和开发节奏梳理成了一份完整的需求文档。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# NorthCombat 模组开发日志：从零构建一款战术FPS模组的设计蓝图"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"距离在《我的世界》里复刻出接近现代战术射击体验的模组——**NorthCombat**，这个想法诞生已经有一段时间了。经过几轮内部讨论与技术验证，我们最终把整个模组的交互哲学、功能模块、网络协议和开发节奏梳理成了一份完整的需求文档。这篇博客既是归档记录，也是方便团队成员随时对齐认知的“活文档”。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"1-核心理念让指令从玩家视野中彻底消失"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. 核心理念：让指令从玩家视野中彻底消失"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"传统模组，尤其是多人竞技模组，往往要求玩家记忆大量指令"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/join/create/ready"},{"type":"text","text":"……这在快节奏对战中非常割裂。NorthCombat 的设计第一原则就是“零指令”。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"玩家的唯一交互入口是一件物品——战术终端。它固定在物品栏的第9格，无法丢弃、无法移动，死亡后自动恢复。右键打开后，一个基于 MCEF 的内置浏览器会加载我们的平台官网。后续所有操作——签到、建房、匹配、查看数据——都在这个网页中点击完成。网页通过 JavaScript 桥接调用模组能力，模组再通过网络包与服务端交互。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"对管理员（OP）来说，后台指令依然保留，但对普通玩家完全透明。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"2-官网功能全景图"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 官网功能"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"网页端承担了几乎全部“大厅系统”的职能，我们把它划分为9大模块："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 签到 | 每日打卡，连续签到递增奖励 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 活动 | 限时/节日任务，一键参与，自动结算 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 建房 | 自定义模式、地图、密码、人数、排位开关与规则参数 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 排位 | 段位、ELO、赛季数据、历史对局详情 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 背包 | 搜打撤装备仓库、武器配置、保险箱管理 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 好友 | 增删好友、邀请、在线状态 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 排行榜 | 全服/赛季排名，多维度排行 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"| 商店 | 皮肤、通行证、虚拟货币充值 |"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"每个模块都对应独立的网页面板，通过左侧导航栏切换，右侧动态渲染内容，实现类似桌面应用的操作体验。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"3-建房流程从表单到房间实例"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. 建房流程：从表单到房间实例"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"建房是完全在网页内闭环的，流程如下："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. 玩家点击“创建房间”，弹出面板；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 选择模式（死斗/TDM/竞技/搜打撤）、地图（从服务端实时拉取列表）、最大人数、可选密码、是否排位，以及自定义规则（回合时间、击杀上限等）；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. 点击“创建”按钮，网页调用 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"NorthCombat.createRoom(configJson)"},{"type":"text","text":"；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. 模组发送 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_CREATE_ROOM"},{"type":"text","text":" 包到服务端，服务端验证权限后创建房间实例；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. 网页自动跳转至“我的房间”面板，展示房间号、当前玩家列表、房主专属的“开始游戏”和“邀请好友”按钮，以及每位玩家的准备状态。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这种设计让建房与匹配在体验上完全统一，无需离开终端屏幕。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"-4-排位与对局记录数据可追溯"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":" 4. 排位与对局记录：数据可追溯"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"排位信息页不再只是一张静态图，而是动态仪表板："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 当前段位图标与名称；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- ELO 进度条（显示当前分数与升级门槛）；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 赛季关键指标：场次、胜率、KD、ADR、爆头率等等；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 最近10场对局缩略列表（可展开完整详情）；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 段位历史折线图；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 赛季剩余倒计时与奖励预览。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"对局记录则更偏向复盘分析："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 列表视图：时间、模式、地图、结果、得分、时长；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 详情视图：双方完整玩家列表、个人数据（击杀/死亡/助攻/伤害/经济）、击杀位置热区图（计划用 Canvas 绘制）、下载回放按钮；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 若玩家正在对局中，该页面会实时推送比分、存活状态、回合历史和经济曲线（竞技模式专属），为观众或教练提供数据支持。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"-5-网络包协议客户端与服务端的共同语言"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":" 5. 网络包协议：客户端与服务端的共同语言"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"为了低耦合与可维护性，我们严格区分包的方向与职责。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"客户端 → 服务端"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_"},{"type":"text","text":" 系列）："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_MATCH_REQUEST"},{"type":"text","text":" – 快速匹配"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_CREATE_ROOM"},{"type":"text","text":" – 创建房间（附带完整 JSON 配置）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_JOIN_ROOM"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_LEAVE_ROOM"},{"type":"text","text":" – 房间进出"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_KICK_PLAYER"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_START_GAME"},{"type":"text","text":" – 房主权限"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_PLAYER_READY"},{"type":"text","text":" – 准备/取消准备"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_DAILY_CHECKIN"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_CLAIM_REWARD"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_CLAIM_ACTIVITY"},{"type":"text","text":" – 活动与签到"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_INVITE_FRIEND"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_ACCEPT_INVITE"},{"type":"text","text":" – 好友邀请"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_SEND_CHAT"},{"type":"text","text":" – 游戏内文本通信"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_UPDATE_SETTING"},{"type":"text","text":" – 客户端设置同步"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_BUY_ITEM"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_PLANT_BOMB"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_DEFUSE_BOMB"},{"type":"text","text":" – 竞技模式核心机制"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_EXTRACT"},{"type":"text","text":" – 搜打撤撤离"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"服务端 → 客户端"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_"},{"type":"text","text":" 系列）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ROOM_CREATED"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ROOM_UPDATED"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ROOM_LIST"},{"type":"text","text":" – 房间状态同步"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_MATCH_FOUND"},{"type":"text","text":" – 匹配成功，分配队伍"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_PLAYER_JOINED_ROOM"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_PLAYER_LEFT_ROOM"},{"type":"text","text":" – 玩家进出通知"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ALL_READY"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_GAME_START"},{"type":"text","text":" – 倒计时与开赛"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_GAME_STATE"},{"type":"text","text":" – 对局全局状态"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_SYNC_PLAYER_DATA"},{"type":"text","text":" – 经济、弹药、生命等关键数据"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_DEATH_EVENT"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_KILLCAM_DATA"},{"type":"text","text":" – 击杀与死亡回放"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_SPAWN_PROTECTION"},{"type":"text","text":" – 出生保护"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ROUND_START"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ROUND_END"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_MATCH_END"},{"type":"text","text":" – 回合生命周期"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_BUY_MENU_OPEN"},{"type":"text","text":" – 购买阶段触发"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_BOMB_PLANTED"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_BOMB_DEFUSED"},{"type":"text","text":" – 炸弹状态"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_EXTRACTION_ZONE"},{"type":"text","text":" – 撤离点信息"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_CHECKIN_RESULT"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_CLAIM_RESULT"},{"type":"text","text":" – 活动结算"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_RANK_DATA"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_LEADERBOARD"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_FRIEND_LIST"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_INVITE_RECEIVED"},{"type":"text","text":" – 社交与数据"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_SETTING_SYNC"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_ERROR"},{"type":"text","text":" – 同步与错误处理"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"每个网络包都会实现为独立文件，方便后续扩展与多人协作。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"-6-网页端-UI-布局与桥接-API"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"6. 网页端 UI 布局与桥接 API"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"界面结构遵循经典的仪表板式设计："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 顶部栏：显示玩家头像、昵称、段位勋章、虚拟货币余额；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 左侧导航（图标+文字）：首页、签到、活动中心、快速匹配、创建房间、排位赛、对局记录、我的背包、好友、排行榜、设置、关闭终端；"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 右侧内容区：根据导航项动态切换，保留面包屑导航。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"-7-管理员工具与地图管理"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"7. 管理员工具与地图管理"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"虽然普通玩家完全无感，但服务器维护离不开 OP 指令。我们保留了6条核心命令："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/tc stop"},{"type":"text","text":" – 强制结束当前对局"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/tc setlobby <radius>"},{"type":"text","text":" – 设定大厅保护区半径"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/tc map create <id>"},{"type":"text","text":" / "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"delete <id>"},{"type":"text","text":" – 动态管理地图"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/tc map wand <id> <team>"},{"type":"text","text":" – 使用选区工具设置队伍出生点"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/tc reload"},{"type":"text","text":" – 热重载配置文件"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"/tc debug <on/off>"},{"type":"text","text":" – 开启或关闭调试日志输出"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这些命令只在后台执行，不会出现在任何面向玩家的界面中。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"-8-分阶段开发计划共8个阶段"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"8. 分阶段开发计划（共8个阶段）"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"为了控制复杂度，我们按依赖关系拆解成8个冲刺阶段："}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"1. 基础框架：主类、网络包注册机制、配置文件加载、管理员命令骨架。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"2. 核心系统：GameState 状态机、MatchManager 与 MatchInstance 生命周期、TeamManager / Team 数据结构。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"3. 战术终端：特殊物品实现、第9格锁定逻辑（包含防丢弃、防移动、死亡恢复）、全面的物品保护拦截。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"4. 浏览器界面：MCEF 屏幕渲染、JS 桥接对象 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"NorthCombat"},{"type":"text","text":" 的方法注册与回调推送。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"5. 全部网络包：逐一实现所有 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"C_"},{"type":"text","text":" 和 "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"code"}],"text":"S_"},{"type":"text","text":" 包，每个包独立文件，编写单元测试。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"6. 平台通信：HTTP 客户端封装，对接外部平台 API（签到奖励、排位数据拉取、商店查询等）。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"7. TACZ 集成：兼容 Timeless and Classics Guns 模组，构建虚拟装备系统，支撑搜打撤模式的进/出局装备逻辑。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"8. 游戏模式：抽象模式接口，依次实现死斗、TDM、竞技（含经济系统与炸弹逻辑）、搜打撤四种模式。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2,"id":"-结语"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"结语"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这份文档就是 NorthCombat 的“圣经”，后续所有的代码提交、界面设计、测试用例都将围绕它展开。目前我们已经进入了第1阶段的开发，基础框架搭建完毕后，会通过 博客 持续更新进展。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"如果你也是 Minecraft 模组开发者，或者对战术射击游戏的系统设计感兴趣，欢迎关注本系列的后续内容。也欢迎在评论区留下你的建议——比如“搜打撤的保险箱机制如何设计才平衡”，我们很乐意一起探讨。"}]},{"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"italic"}],"text":"NorthCombat，让方块世界也能弥漫硝烟与战术。"}]}]}